15 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the outstanding contributions of this
16 exemplary veteran are appropriately honored.
17 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
18 recognize and commend Shelly-Ann Simpson for the dedication, bravery, and sacrifices she
19 has made to serve her country and extend sincere best wishes for her continued health,
20 happiness, and success.
